App Privacy Information

Privacy Policy: Our app is committed to respecting and protecting your privacy. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, and safeguard your personal information. By downloading and using our app, you consent to the practices described in this policy.

Data Collection and Usage:

Personal Information: We may collect some personally identifiable information such as names, email addresses, or contact details. This information helps us to authenticate users and also to sent notifications.
Permissions:
Device Information: We do not collect any device-specific information, including your device model, operating system version, and unique device identifiers. This information helps us troubleshoot issues and improve the app's performance.
Permissions:

Camera and Photos: Our app may request access to your device's camera and photos for specific features. This permission is necessary to provide functionality such as capturing images within the app.
Location: We do not request access to your device's location.
Data Sharing:

Third-Party Services: We do not share any user data with third-party services or advertisers.
Data Security:

Encryption: Any data that is transmitted between your device and our servers is encrypted using industry-standard protocols.
Secure Storage: Any data that is stored on our servers is stored securely with appropriate access controls.
Opt-Out Options:

Our app does not engage in data collection for advertising or analytics purposes.
Contact Information:

If you have any questions or concerns about your privacy while using our app, please feel free to contact us at privacy@example.com.
Updates:

Any updates or changes to our privacy policy will be posted on this page.
